body: It was..an interesting ARAM. Let me know what you think!

replies.body:
Cos nothing is wrong with 14 year olds talking about genitals.
#newage

what's with the squeaker.

Well I'll start by saying we're all 20+ and as for the squeaker, if you mean me *coughs* I am a female human, if you don't, I honestly don't know to whom you are referring. {{sticker:slayer-jinx-wink}}

Okay, glad the first part got explained.
The person who barely speaks, yet squeaks, is that you? If so, no offence intended, I pictured a 11 year old kid with glasses.
I'll drink to that.

PS: Only watched it to 1 minute 20 second - I felt uncomfortable after the genital talk :(

{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-rainbows}}
Haha, if you mean in green text (I'm white) I think I know what you mean, he does that a bit on purpose. When he talks a lot there's a lot of range there I guess. I just never really noticed it :)

Okay, I watched the video in its whole entirety, yes, the squeaker is now confirmed female.
Well, there's voice changers out there - but hey, I'm optimistic.

Sorry for the negativity - that's just how I roll.

{{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}}
No worries m8, you do you :) Voice changers are a lot of effort, but I'm sure that's what someone using a voice changer would say :)
